msgid ""
"To Configure Envoy to record statistics for inbound or outbound traffic, "
"add the ``sidecar.istio.io/statsInclusionPrefixes`` annotation to the pod"
" template in the Kubernetes ``Deployment``. Add the ``cluster.outbound`` "
"prefix to gather data about outbound traffic activity and circuit "
"breaking. To gather data on inbound traffic, add the ``listener`` prefix."
" The sample `fortio-deploy.yaml "
"<%7B%7B%3C%20github_file%3E%7D%7D/samples/httpbin/sample-client/fortio-"
"deploy.yaml>`_ shows use of ``sidecar.istio.io/statsInclusionPrefixes`` "
"with the ``cluster.outbound`` prefix."
msgstr ""

